snippet.title: Yugo Puzzle Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Yugo Puzzle is a new puzzle game from the creator of Jelly no Puzzle. The game is planned to be released in 2021.

Website: https://qrostar.skr.jp/en/yugo/
日本語ウェブサイト: https://qrostar.skr.jp/yugo/
